            <p class="plink"><a class="introduce pull-left" href="#myModal" role="button" data-toggle="modal">更多风险评估理论介绍</a></p>
            <br><a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href="/userrisktolerance/p3steps">开 始 风 险 评 估</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span4 offset1">
          <a href="#myModal_pic" role="button" data-toggle="modal"><img src="/assets/userrisktolerance-1.jpg"></a>
          <p> </p>
